Task
Is it true that the given number is a negative odd number?
Given an arbitrary number. Determine if it is a negative odd number.
Create a variable number and assign it the value of an arbitrary integer. Create a variable isNegativeOdd and assign 
it a boolean expression that evaluates to true if the number is odd and negative, and false otherwise.

Solution
const number = -9;
const isNegativeOdd = number % 2 !== 0 && number < 0;
